FBIS3-21757 "jptdd010__l94062" JPRS-TDD-94-010L Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Narcotics 7 March 1994 NEAR EAST & SOUTH ASIA ISRAEL Smugglers of 2 Kg of Heroin Sentenced in Haifa TA2602181894 TA2602181894 Article Type:BFN [Editorial Report] Tel Aviv HA'ARETZ in Hebrew on 25 February, in a page A9 reported by ITIM, states: "Two heroin smugglers from the Galilee village of Julis, Daniyel 'Amad Mukhtar, 25, and 'Amad Nayif Hasan, 30, were sentenced by the Haifa District court to six years imprisonment after being convicted of smuggling 2 kg of heroin from Lebanon to Israel. They were apprehended by the police in May 1993
